title: Taiwan Weily Lottery Winners Donate NT$290 Million (Taichung City Government)
text: ( Source : Taichung City Government ) Taiwan Weily Lottery Winners Donate NT$290 Million God of Wealth comes to Taichung! Taiwan Weily Lottery in April 2015 with a prize money of NT$ 3, 003 million, the highest in lottery history, was sold out
